SUMMARY:Information: METROPOLITAN LINE: Saturday 31 May\, until 1600\, no 
 service between Harrow-on-the-Hill and Uxbridge. Use PICCADILLY LINE 
 services between Rayners Lane and Uxbridge. Replacement bus service ML1 
 operates between Stonebridge Park (for Bakerloo and Lioness lines) and 
 Rayners Lane via Wembley Park\, Preston Road\, Northwick Park (Hospital)\,
  Harrow-on-the-Hill\, West Harrow (Pinner Road) and North Harrow (Station 
 Road)
