SUMMARY:Information: METROPOLITAN LINE: Saturday 31 May and Sunday 1 June\,
  no service between Aldgate and Watford. Trains will continue to operate 
 between Harrow-on-the-Hill and Amersham / Chesham\, but operate non-stop 
 between Harrow-on-the-Hill and Moor Park. CHILTERN RAILWAYS services 
 continue to operate between Marylebone and Amersham. Replacement buses 
 operate.
